title: 171: Bucky's Top-5 by position & LSU defensive back interviews
itunes:title: 171: Bucky's Top-5 by position & LSU defensive back interviews
description:
Former NFL Scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down Bucky's latest top-5 prospect list by position groups. The guys then play a game called "Sure, Surprised, or Shocked". They are also joined by top draft prospects and former LSU defensive backs Jamal Adams and Tre'Davious White.
